snippet.title: Cave Story's Secret Santa Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Introducing Cave Story's Secret Santa, a FREE game created by Nicalis in cooperation with Studio Pixel. It's a bite-sized side story of stealth and puzzle solving, available now for a limited time: 
https://bit.ly/CSSS_Steam     https://bit.ly/CSSS_GOG     https://bit.ly/CSSS_Epic
